summary:
Sorry Everyone, I forgot to add my file. Please download and give me some feedback.
______________
This adds a dungeon and a cool world at the end. This is a work in progress so please give it a chance. Take a look at it and tell me what you think... I would love some feedback.
descriptionHtml:
Update #1 - It\'s finally here guys, I have updated my mod. I added 2 more rooms to the mod, I still need to do alot of work, like make more in the rooms and make more in the other world. But please give this mod a chance... Thank you all for downloading the mod (the 22 people that did).
______________
This is a dungeon mod that adds a small dungeon to your game near riverwood. Now this is a work in progress mod but still very cool, I have added a world at the end of the dungeon that you will eventually be able to explor once I get the chance to edit it and add way more things to it. But for now please tell me what I should do different. I know I need to add way more to the dungeon but is my first time making a mod, and I think it is pretty cool. Well hope you enjoy.

____________________
Please check out the video section.
author: GamerTechz
